Usability Testing Report

Summary:
Five users participated in usability testing.

Key Findings:
- Search functionality was not immediately visible.
- Users hesitated during checkout.
- Order tracking lacked clarity.

Recommendations:
1. Move search bar to the top of the home screen.
2. Highlight the checkout button.
3. Add delivery progress updates.

Conclusion:
Implementing these changes will improve overall user experience and task completion rates.
